metadata.description: Discover the intricate harmony of Salmon & Tuna Mosaic Sushi, a visually stunning and flavorful delight. This exceptional sushi showcases a canvas of white rice adorned with a mosaic of smoked salmon pieces, surrounding a premium quality tuna core. Each element is wrapped in nori seaweed and enveloped by a delicate layer of salmon. Topped with three dollops of Japanese mayonnaise and black sesame seeds, this dish is truly a feast for the eyes and the taste buds.
metadata.name: Salmon & Tuna Mosaic Sushi #65 #1/6
